Uses of Package
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity This package contains classes which define the various BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support This package contains classes which support various BPEL activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.convert.visitors This package contains visitors which are used to convert from one version of BPEL to another. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io This package contains the BPEL reader and writer interfaces and the factory classes to access them. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefReader interface for reading in BPEL xml and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefWriter interface for serializing specific AeBaseDef object subclasses and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation This package contains classes which support BPEL validation.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity This package contains implementation classes for activity validation models. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.assign This package contains validation model classes for validating the assign activity. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.decision This package contains validation model implementation classes for if, elseif, and else constructs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.links This package contains implementation classes for link-related validation models (such as source, target, link, etc...). 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.scope This package contains validation model implementation classes for scope related validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.wsio This package contains validation model implementation classes for WSIO related validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expressions This package contains validation model implementation classes for expression based validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.preprocess.strategies.wsio Visitors and supporting classes for determining the proper strategy for wsio activities and their message data production or consumption. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity This package contains classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign This package contains implementation objects used for executing the assign activity. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign.from This package contains implementation classes used when executing the 'from' portion of an assign activity's copy operation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign.to This package contains implementation classes used when executing the 'to' portion of an assign activity's copy operation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support Includes supporting bpel objects which aren't properly activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.consume Provides interfaces and classes for consuming WSDL message data by BPEL activities and other supporting objects (e.g., invoke activity, receive activity, and onEvent element of a pick activity).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.produce Provides interfaces and classes for producing WSDL message data from BPEL activities (e.g., invoke and reply).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy Process deployment.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate Root package for the Active Endpoints BPEL Deployment Validation code.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview This package contains all the code and presentation beans for driving the web app Process Details view ui.
